Brief installation instructions 
VADR 0.991dev; October 2019
-------------------------------------------------------------

These are quick installation instructions. For complete documentation,
including customization and troubleshooting, please see the
file vadr/documentation/install.md

Copy https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nawrockie/vadr/master/vadr-install.sh
to a new empty directory where you want to install VADR and execute
the following command in that directory:

./vadr-install.sh linux

OR

./vadr-install.sh macosx

Depending if you are installing on a Linux or Mac/OSX system.

Set your envirnoment variables as explained at the end of the output
of the above command.

Run tests to verify that your installation was successful by
running the command:

$VADRSCRIPTSDIR/testfiles/do-install-tests-local.sh

